  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645570/extras/53a19467515c899385608effddb7d27e.gif?t=1679690764\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645570/extras/53a19467515c899385608effddb7d27e.poster.avif?t=1679690764\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>Greedy Bubble is a brutally difficult arcade game about greediness inside a cave. In this game, you control a cute bubble that is trapped inside a cave, you need to guide it out while collecting as many coins as you can ( and not loosing them ). Avoid spikes, saws and use teleporters, air pressure and others to escape.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 brutally difficult levels.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro graphics ( 80's style ).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Good chiptune music to get yourself vibing :)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645570/extras/53a19467515c899385608effddb7d27e.gif?t=1679690764\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645570/extras/53a19467515c899385608effddb7d27e.poster.avif?t=1679690764\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>Greedy Bubble is a brutally difficult arcade game about greediness inside a cave. In this game, you control a cute bubble that is trapped inside a cave, you need to guide it out while collecting as many coins as you can ( and not loosing them ). Avoid spikes, saws and use teleporters, air pressure and others to escape.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 brutally difficult levels.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro graphics ( 80's style ).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Good chiptune music to get yourself vibing :)</li></ul>",
